# Pin npm to the public registry for this repo.
#
# Rationale: this personal repo must not resolve packages through any
# employer-owned mirror. The user's global ~/.npmrc points at an internal
# Artifactory URL that is unreachable from GitHub Actions and would leak
# into the lockfile if left unpinned. This local .npmrc wins over the
# user-scoped one for anything run inside this repo.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
